    <title>包含SLB的环境缩容时提示some of the specified backend servers do not exist or are not running.</title>
    <link href="http://brianchenl.github.io/2022/05/26/%E5%8C%85%E5%90%ABSLB%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%BC%A9%E5%AE%B9%E6%97%B6%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BAsome-of-the-specified-backend-servers-do-not-exist-or-are-not-running/"/>
    <id>http://brianchenl.github.io/2022/05/26/%E5%8C%85%E5%90%ABSLB%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E7%BC%A9%E5%AE%B9%E6%97%B6%E6%8F%90%E7%A4%BAsome-of-the-specified-backend-servers-do-not-exist-or-are-not-running/</id>
    <published>2022-05-26T12:21:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-05-27T14:46:25.412Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="问题现场"><a href="#问题现场" class="headerlink" title="问题现场"></a>问题现场</h3><p>使用<a href="https://www.cloudiac.org/" title="CloudIaC官网">CloudIaC</a>供给了一套高可用环境，SLB关联多个ECS instance。用户量下降后，根据需求减少ECS instance实例数量，执行环境更新操作时，给报错了。</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ansible_host.cloudiac_website[1]: Destroying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=10.9.0.110]</span><br><span class="line">ansible_host.cloudiac_website[1]: Destruction complete after 0s</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Destroying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=i-j6cfxch3hp19qbdi10dc]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Still destroying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=i-j6cfxch3hp19qbdi10dc, 10s elapsed]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Destruction complete after 12s</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_slb_server_group.default: Modifying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=rsp-j6ctarh6aaavt]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Error: [ERROR] terraform-provider-alicloud/alicloud/resource_alicloud_slb_server_group.go:209: Resource rsp-j6ctarh6aaavt RemoveVServerGroupBackendServers Failed!!! [SDK alibaba-cloud-sdk-go ERROR]:</span><br><span class="line">SDK.ServerError</span><br><span class="line">ErrorCode: ObtainIpFail</span><br><span class="line">Recommend: https://next.api.aliyun.com/troubleshoot?q=ObtainIpFail&amp;product=Slb</span><br><span class="line">RequestId: 97B9EA25-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-0ABE26C845B4</span><br><span class="line">Message: The specified BackendServers is invalid; some of the specified backend servers <span class="keyword">do</span> not exist or are not running.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  on main.tf line 70, <span class="keyword">in</span> resource <span class="string">&quot;alicloud_slb_server_group&quot;</span> <span class="string">&quot;default&quot;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  70: resource <span class="string">&quot;alicloud_slb_server_group&quot;</span> <span class="string">&quot;default&quot;</span> &#123;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>第二次执行就成功。</p><h3 id="问题分析"><a href="#问题分析" class="headerlink" title="问题分析"></a>问题分析</h3><p>从日志中可以看到，先做了instance [id&#x3D;10.9.0.110] 的释放，再去更新slb_server_group资源时报了错。从控制台操作逻辑来说，应该是先将需要释放的instance从slb服务器组中删除，再进行销毁。应该是这个处理逻辑错乱出的错。给阿里云提工单！！</p><h3 id="解决结果"><a href="#解决结果" class="headerlink" title="解决结果"></a>解决结果</h3><p>2个月后的今天，阿里云终于给出了已修复的答复，试了下还是老问题，询问后得知需要增加一个资源配置，修改代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">resource <span class="string">&quot;alicloud_slb_server_group&quot;</span> <span class="string">&quot;default&quot;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  load_balancer_id = alicloud_slb_load_balancer.default.id</span><br><span class="line">  name             = <span class="string">&quot;cloudiac_server_group&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 注释掉原代码</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># servers &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#   server_ids = alicloud_instance.cloudiac.*.id</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#   port       = &quot;80&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#   weight     = 50</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># &#125;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">resource <span class="string">&quot;alicloud_slb_server_group_server_attachment&quot;</span> <span class="string">&quot;ssga&quot;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  count = var.instance_number</span><br><span class="line">  server_group_id = alicloud_slb_server_group.default.id</span><br><span class="line">  server_id = alicloud_instance.cloudiac[count.index].<span class="built_in">id</span></span><br><span class="line">  port = <span class="string">&quot;80&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  weight = 50</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>缩容执行结果：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ansible_host.cloudiac_website[1]: Destroying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=10.9.0.111]</span><br><span class="line">ansible_host.cloudiac_website[1]: Destruction complete after 0s</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_slb_server_group_server_attachment.ssga[1]: Destroying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=rsp-j6ctarh6aaavt:i-j6c5hdcgb6fim7vq3vxe:80]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_slb_listener.default: Modifying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=lb-j6cmx0wqg117iobg0pq00:https:443]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_slb_server_group_server_attachment.ssga[1]: Destruction complete after 0s</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Destroying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=i-j6c5hdcgb6fim7vq3vxe]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_slb_listener.default: Modifications complete after 1s [<span class="built_in">id</span>=lb-j6cmx0wqg117iobg0pq00:https:443]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_slb_listener.http: Modifying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=lb-j6cmx0wqg117iobg0pq00:http:80]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_slb_listener.http: Modifications complete after 1s [<span class="built_in">id</span>=lb-j6cmx0wqg117iobg0pq00:http:80]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Still destroying... [<span class="built_in">id</span>=i-j6c5hdcgb6fim7vq3vxe, 10s elapsed]</span><br><span class="line">alicloud_instance.instance[1]: Destruction complete after 12s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以看到，在instance销毁之前，先做了 alicloud_slb_server_group_server_attachment 资源的变更，至此问题修复。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
